message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and audio processing. Other likely categories could be cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.NE. cs.LG and cs.AI deal with machine learning and deep learning, which are used in the proposed methodology. cs.CV deals with computer vision, which can be applied to audio analysis. cs.NE deals with neural networks, which are used in the deep learning-based monophonic event classifier.
